  <description>
    <localized-text>
      <locale language="en">Creates a task for the default work queue when the system is unable to determine a supervisor dynamically for a case after the case has been submitted for approval. The task is assigned to the work queue so that the user working on the task can set a supervisor for the case manually. The process also notifies the administrator and all subscribers of the work queue that a task has been assigned to the work queue as the system could not determine a supervisor dynamically.</locale>
